{"tid":2044646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會調查：9成9人反對國安法 逾6成人支持以「香港獨立」為最終抗爭目標","createTime":"2020-05-31T08:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T14:41:53.000Z","uid":36494,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf270f20ed3ab911975ba6f3ce79801cb926c42","tid":2044646,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073889&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdLBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=c9d4c4fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073889&h=7ed0b59c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073889</a>"},{"pid":"ae69aec0b5487337dda0aa24d4d9d120b050b608","tid":2044646,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f406c31f603ffbe0f1eefdb56391dc97f79bc043","tid":2044646,"uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"全國人大昨日投票，通過訂立「港版國安法」。民間記者會晚上公佈民意調查結果，是次調查破紀錄獲<span style=\"color: red;\">超過37萬人回應</span>，當中<span style=\"color: red;\">近9成9受訪者反對在港實施《國安法》</span>；雖然社會瀰漫悲觀情緒，但仍有逾7萬名受訪者表示會繼續參與最高危的「前線行動」。<br />\n<br />\n受訪者普遍悲觀 憂港設國安機構<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會於本月23日至25日就港版國安法進行問卷調查，破紀錄獲超過37萬人回覆，受訪者主要為16至45歲的全職人士和學生。結果顯示，近9成9人反對在港實施《國安法》，超過3分2受訪者對《國安法》持負面情緒，例如憤怒、討厭和憎恨。以10分為滿分，<span style=\"color: red;\">受訪者對香港整體及抗爭前景分別只給予2.84分和4.7分</span>。有逾9成人擔心北京會在港設立國安機構，以極端及非法手段打壓異見人士，如「送中」、行私刑等，更憂慮港府會藉此推行愛國洗腦教育。<br />\n<br />\n逾6成人支持香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會發言人指，縱然《國歌法》「有如壓頸利刄」製造白色恐怖，但從調查結果可見抗爭者爭取自由的決心依然堅定，<span style=\"color: red;\">超過6成人認為要繼續進行大罷工、捐助抗爭基金、支持良心經濟圈等，更有逾7萬人表明會繼續參與最高危的「前線行動」。發言人認為港人仍具備「長久戰的決心」，近8成人贊成「攬炒」，更有逾6成、即約23萬受訪者支持以「香港獨立」為最終抗爭目標。</span><br />\n<br />\n前日警方於旺角和銅鑼灣等地大舉拘捕示威者，發言人指「我哋已經退無可退 」，又認為示威者前日行動缺乏清晰目標，強調港人要團結，繼續以香港民族的身份堅持抗爭。"},{"pid":"d0bc3c7a68e2b7770a34adf7ee46e441991ada4f","tid":2044646,"uid":51583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:43:37.000Z","msg":"其實又冇咩意思<br />\n兩邊D數字都係自己既支持者去做<br />\n都係立會投票最真實"},{"pid":"cc9e9ac4a4ff710f5dbfa9875a854a24bc1443de","tid":2044646,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"超過6成人認為要繼續進行大罷工、捐助抗爭基金、支持良心經濟圈等，更有逾7萬人表明會繼續參與最高危的「前線行動」。發言人認為港人仍具備「長久戰的決心」，近8成人贊成「攬炒」，更有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">逾6成、即約23萬受訪者支持以「香港獨立」為最終抗爭目標。</span></span>"},{"pid":"82a6214e5d45e7dbaa882f9a5f79cfa8db1fd15e","tid":2044646,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67eca8c451b607b154f40b053e93902357a7d276","tid":2044646,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5ec82891424fdf8f99f485ccd2d00807e26879","tid":2044646,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5927ce6352b21059d9750495da05faca0ed7ad81","tid":2044646,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"跟我嗌一次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港獨立</strong></span></span><img src=\"